		{
			dependencies: ["7EA5A95D900AE893"]
			description: [
				"Crafting is the most important mechanic in the game, it is the beginning of all the mechanics of the modpack, because without it it is not possible to create tools or machines."
				""
				"The crafting table has a changed crafting in this modpack, however, making it is very simple, use 2x &5Logs&r and 2x &5Flints&r."
				""
				"&a⚠ Tip:&r Flint can be obtained by breaking gravel or by crafting using 3x &5Gravel&r"
			]
			id: "6F564216B9F32497"
			rewards: [
				{
