		{
			dependencies: ["6F564216B9F32497"]
			description: [
				"To be able to get your first ores you need at least stone tools. Stone tools are the link between the minerals and the player, so without them it is not possible to get your first ores."
				""
				"The recipe hasn't changed, don't get too attached to them either, once you make your &5Seared Melter&r you'll have access to better tool materials."
				""
				"&a⚠ Tip:&r vanilla tools after stone have their durability changed to 1, where their only function is to serve as a crafting ingredient."
			]
