		{
			dependencies: ["1388452A2332908E"]
			description: [
				"Ores are the source of any machinery, and you need to store a lot of them."
				""
				"&e-&r All machines or magical rituals require at least some ores in their crafting tree, ores also make alloys that are used in components of more advanced machines."
				""
				"Mining in the modpack is not boring, for example, you can find some &9veins&r of resources throughout the world, so gather lots of resources to have fun and remember to enjoy every moment in the Techpack!"
				""
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"The techpack's ores generation is different from the others, ores have a different spawn quantity depending on the &9temperature&r of the biomes. In general, the amount of ores has increased"
				""
				"&e-&r You can check the chances of finding them by pressing &9U&r on an ore block or raw item"
				""
				"&e-&r The modpack guide has a page dedicated to explaining this feature, with spawning chances and which biomes have specific temperatures"
			]
			icon: "minecraft:raw_iron"
			id: "1B935334CB080110"
			rewards: [
				{
					count: 16
					id: "0EE0ABE930987BAF"
