			description: [
				"just store your previously collected resources"
				""
				"&e-&r Keep in mind that in Techpack, plates and gears are used a lot, so a good way out would be to store your resources in fluids, so that it is easier to mold them into plates through Tinkers"
				""
				"&e-&r At this point, the best tank you can have is the &9Tinker's construct&r's tank, but don't worry, as soon as you have access to bronze you can craft the create's tank"
